 MASON HILL ADVISORS Overview



												   Mason Hill Advisors Llc is a hedge fund that manages 1.5 BN dollars in regulatory AUM and has 17 employees, of which 8 perform investment advisory functions. The manager's has disclosed holdings from 12/31/06 to 03/31/17. The fund's latest filing disclosed 24MM in positions, representing 2% of the manager's regulatory AUM.
												



